  "instructions": [
    "Wash and dry the endive and red cabbage, then cut them into thin strips.",
    "Slice the fennel and separate the layers.",
    "In a small bowl, mix the brandy, lemon juice, olive oil, garlic, and salt.",
    "Toss the endive, red cabbage, and fennel with the brandy mixture until well coated.",
    "Sprinkle the pomegranate seeds and parsley over the top.",
    "Serve immediately and garnish with additional parsley if desired.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Refrigerate for at least 30 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
